data.title: 8550 A1A S UNIT 34247, Saint Augustine, FL 32080
data.meta_description: Zillow has 23 photos of this $550,000 2 beds, 3 baths, 1,064 Square Feet condo home located at 8550 A1A S UNIT 34247, Saint Augustine, FL 32080 built in 1982. MLS #2020066.
data.text: Indulge in coastal living at its finest with this stunning ocean view townhome! Located in the Summerhouse Community, this condo features 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, beautiful hardwood floors in the main living area, and exceptional views of the pool and ocean! Outside, the community beckons with a wealth of resort-style amenities, including four temperature-controlled pools, four beach walkovers, a pickleball court, tennis courts, racquetball courts, basketball courts, a kids playground, convenient RV/boat parking, and an onsite rental office! Come see why Summerhouse is the most popular complex on the island!
